- `/knowledge/` — read-only KB links
- `/skills/system/` — read-only platform skills (when mounted)
- `/skills/agent/` — read-only agent-local skills (when mounted)
- `/uploads/` — user files
- `/workspace/` — persistent thread working directory
- `/scratch/` — temporary only
